dct_description_sm: Lucas Ioẽs Aurigarius Inventor ; Ioannes à Doetinckum, fecit.
2 bar scales on map, given in "Hispanica. = Spaensche mylen" and "Germanica = Duÿtzsche mÿlen."
Decorative cartouches and border, coats of arms.
Shows topography, coastline, drainage, shoals, depths, settlements (including ports).

4 profile views: Facies Hollandiæ Australis inter Harlemiam et Scheuelingam, dum præternavigatur ... -- Terra inter Scheuelingam et Mosam ... -- Gedaente vant Landt van Voorn ... -- Terræ Sierixeanæ facies dum e regione tui est ...
Appears in Waghenaer's Spieghel der Zeevaerdt, Leiden:Christophe Plantin, 1584-1588.
